32#ifndef _NOUVEAU_NOUVEAUFB_H_
33#define _NOUVEAU_NOUVEAUFB_H_
34
35#include <sys/bus.h>
36
37#include <drm/drmP.h>
38#include <drm/drm_fb_helper.h>
39
40struct nouveaufb_attach_args {
41 struct drm_device *nfa_drm_dev;
42 struct drm_fb_helper *nfa_fb_helper;
43 struct drm_fb_helper_surface_size nfa_fb_sizes;
44 volatile void *nfa_fb_ptr;
45 uint32_t nfa_fb_linebytes;
46};
47
48#endif /* _NOUVEAU_NOUVEAUFB_H_ */
